snippet.title: Signal & Echo: Iris is Missing TRAILER
snippet.description:
STEAM: tinyurl.com/553ach64 
ITCH.IO: https://tinyurl.com/4fj75hmp 

Signal & Echo: Iris is Missing is a point-and-click adventure with a unique text parser system that enables real detective work. Help Ollie, a wannabe journalist on work experience at the Signal & Echo newspaper, impress his new colleagues by finding out what happened to missing schoolgirl Iris Wood. 

Music by Scott Holmes (www.scottholmesmusic.com)
